claim: Vaccination with a higher-dose recombinant flu vaccine may induce a more robust antibody response than egg-based standard-dose vaccines.
explanation: Top portion of a journal article showing the Elsevier logo, journal name 'Vaccine', ScienceDirect notice, and journal homepage URL; it contains no study data or figures. does not support the claim because the image only shows the journal header and contains no data or comparative results regarding antibody responses to different influenza vaccines
